le Neo, which will also be ported to the Graphene theme. We&#8217;ve also been hard at work on making our all our themes even better. But today, we&#8217;re announcing a new opportunity for [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Syahir Hakim\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2899:\"<p>We&#8217;ve been on a quite a roll here at Graphene themes. A few days ago we announced <a title=\"Feature Highlight: Infinite scroll, better colour presets management\" href=\"http://www.graphene-theme.com/announcement/feature-highlight-infinite-scroll-better-colour-presets-management/\">premium feature addition</a> to Graphene Mobile Neo, which will also be ported to the Graphene theme. We&#8217;ve also been hard at work on making our all our themes even better. But today, we&#8217;re announcing a new opportunity for the Graphene themes community &#8211; our affiliates program.</p>\n<h3>An affiliate program designed for you</h3>\n<p>We&#8217;ve designed our affiliates program to benefit the participants. For starters, we&#8217;re giving out standard 20% commission on all sales generated by leads sent to our website by our affiliates. As your contribution volume gets higher, we&#8217;ll even consider increasing that commission rate.</p>\n<p>And we&#8217;ll make it easy for you to earn commission on prospective buyers. Our affiliates program has a 15-day cookie period. This means that you&#8217;ll earn commission for any purchases made by prospective buyers that you sent our way within 15 days of referral date. That&#8217;ll ensure any purchase originating from your referral will be credited to you.</p>\n<p>On top of that, if you write a review on any of our premium products, we&#8217;ll also provide you with a unique coupon code for 10% discount off the list price of all our products for your readers. Such reviews must be fair and reasonable, but we don&#8217;t require the reviews to be positive. As long as you observe good publishing ethics, we&#8217;ll provide you with the coupon code.</p>\n<p>We have also created four sets of image banners for you to use if you wish, and these are available in the skyscraper dimension (160&#215;600 pixels), medium rectangle (300&#215;250 pixels), large rectangle (336&#215;280 pixels), and leaderboard (728&#215;90 pixels). Those familiar with Google&#8217;s AdSense program will notice that these are the top performing ads dimensions for AdSense.</p>\n<h3>It&#8217;s not an SEO campaign</h3>\n<p>It&#8217;s important to us to let you know that our Affiliates Program is not a search engine optimisation campaign. All our banner codes have the <strong>nofollow</strong> attribute attached to them. This means that your site&#8217;s PageRank value won&#8217;t be passed on to us, and it complies fully with Google&#8217;s referral policy.</p>\n<p>We&#8217;ll be making payments to our affiliates via PayPal, so you must have a PayPal account to participate.</p>\n<p>We&#8217;re looking forward to have you as part of our Affiliates Program, and start generating revenue for yourself and the community!</p>\n<p><a class=\"button\" title=\"Affiliates Program\" href=\"http://www.graphene-theme.com/affiliates/\">Join our Affiliates Program</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:95:\"http://www.graphene-theme.com/announcement/introducing-graphene-themes-affiliates-program/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.or